      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Teterboro%2C_New_Jersey"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "The borough expanded July 5, 1918, annexing land from neighboring Hasbrouck Heights.",
